this endpoint retrieves the Pages and the FAQs that the admin added<br>
to retrieve a page send the `type` param as a JSON palyoad, the param acceps two Values<br>

<strong>PA : </strong> for retrieving Pages.<br>
<strong>FA : </strong> for FAQs <br>

<strong>Body Ex:</strong>:

	{
		"type" : 'PA'
	}

<strong>Response EX :</strong>

	[
		{
			"title": "Privacy Policy",
			"content": "<p>thisis privacy policy page</p>"
		},
		{
			"title": "Notification test",
			"content": ""
		}
	]

<strong>Important : </strong> the values are case sensative, so be carefull when assigning them

